         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00029"/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">XVIII. Spöttelgasse 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00030"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb9814" type="person">M. von Schwind</rs></hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="work" ref="#pmb46835">Die Landpartie – La partie de campagne – The
                     rural excursion</rs> (<rs ref="#pmb9814" type="person">Schwind</rs> u. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10854">Bauernfeld</rs>).</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="center"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00043-B-00003-000-00029"/><rs ref="#pmb45258" type="place">München</rs>. <date>23 VII</date>.</dateline></opener><p>Ganz ähnlich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind wir ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tern u. vorge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tern über <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Sa<subst><del rend="overwritten">z</del><add place="inline">lz</add></subst>burg</rs> hierher gefahren und doch auch wieder unähnlich. Es i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t eine
               Preisaufgabe für <rs ref="#pmb12692" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Heini</hi></rs>, a. die Ähnlichkeit – b.) die Unter<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chiede herauszufinden.<space unit="chars" quantity="3"/>Viele Grüße Euch beiden.</p><closer><signed>Hugo.</signed><lb/><signed><handShift scribe="#pmb16658"/>L. Friedmann</signed><lb/><signed><handShift scribe="#pmb2292"/>Gerty</signed><lb/><signed><handShift scribe="#pmb16670"/>Rose Friedmann</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
